title: Facebook’s $1,000 bonus only applies to full-time employees working from home, not contractors
text: Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg said in an internal memo earlier this week that the company will give employees working from home during the COVID-19 pandemic a $1,000 cash bonus. But, as the Intercept first reported, contractors will not receive the bonus.
